 openly. If thou do these things, shew thyself to the world.","year":33},{"id":"recxWOiIScjvYZ1y1","ref":"John.7.5","text":"For neither did his brethren believe in him.","year":33},{"id":"recoeEehmWuz1AL3v","ref":"John.7.6","text":"Then Jesus said unto them, My time is not yet come: but your time is alway ready.","year":33},{"id":"rec7U0408GZxqVSkL","ref":"John.7.7","text":"The world cannot hate you; but me it hateth, because I testify of it, that the works thereof are evil.","year":33},{"id":"reczjx5CSOTBsrPXm","ref":"John.7.8","text":"Go ye up unto this feast: I go not up yet unto this feast; for my time is not yet full come.","year":33}]}
